# InnerState

InnerStatw is a mobile application for gentle self-reflection and emotional clarity.
The product is not a habit tracker, productivity system, or therapeutic tool.


## Download the APK

You can download the APK directly from Google Drive:

👉 [Download Stillness APK](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1vFBjF0vFzgQ0nuq1U9onYwBgJnFZ1zi2/view?usp=drivesdk)

### How to install (Android)

1. Download the APK file from the link above to your Android device.
2. Open the file manager and locate the downloaded APK.
3. Tap the APK file to start the installation.
4. If prompted, allow installation from unknown sources (you can disable it again afterwards).
5. Once installed, find InnerState in your app list and open it.
